TopicTitle: What do you do when you don't play KSP?

Articles.Content:
What do you do when you don't play KSP?

This thread is for other hobbies that people do outside of KSP.

I for example Scuba Dive with my brother and my Dad of Rottnest island or the Rockingham Dive Trail. I also practice my trumpet for band and my bagpipes for pipe band.
I am on our high school's robotics team. This is our second year so we are still lacking in funding and skill. I'm also the first chair French Horn in our band.
